org.minijson.common

Class CyclicCharArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.minijson.common.CyclicCharArray

  • public final class CyclicCharArray
extends Object
    The purpose of this class is to implement "subarray" operation that does not require the content copy (which requires new memory allocation). Use CharArrayWrapper for "linear" or regular arrays. This class is for wrapping "cyclic" arrays like CharQueue (ring buffer).
